### Get user's orders
GET http://localhost:8000/api/orders/user/1
Authorization: Bearer token

### Get orders by status
GET http://localhost:8000/api/orders/status/pending
Authorization: Bearer token

### Create new order
POST http://localhost:8000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer token

{
  "userId": 1,
  "totalAmount": 99.99,
  "shippingAddress": "123 Main St, Nairobi",
  "contactPhone": "+254712345678"
}

### Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/orders/5
Authorization: Bearer token

### Update order status
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/orders/5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer token

{
  "status": "shipped",
  "trackingNumber": "TRK123456"
}

### Cancel order
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/orders/5/cancel
Authorization: Bearer token